Class ContentBlock9ViewHolder.MarkerCallback

    public class ContentBlock9ViewHolder.MarkerCallback
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.squareup.picasso.Callback
    Callback is needed to load the spotImage async with picasso. InfoWindow is drawn and cannot be updated after loading the image. This callback will hide and show the infoWindow after loading the image, so that it gets redrawn and the image will be shown.
